@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home page";
}



<div class="container">
    <h1>Discover Your Perfect Furniture</h1>

    <p class="lead">
        Welcome to our furniture website, where style meets comfort!
    </p>

    <hr class="my-4">

    <p>
        At our online store, we take pride in offering a handpicked collection of exquisite furniture pieces
        that will transform your living spaces into inviting havens. From modern and chic designs to timeless classics,
        our furniture range caters to your unique tastes and preferences.
    </p>

    <p>
        Explore our thoughtfully curated selection of comfortable chairs, sturdy tables, elegant sofas, and much more.
        Each piece is crafted with attention to detail and quality, ensuring that your furniture stands the test of time.
    </p>

    <p>
        We believe that choosing furniture should be an enjoyable experience. That's why we've designed our website
        to be user-friendly and intuitive, making it effortless for you to find the perfect furniture for your home or office.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-5">Our Technology Stack</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <strong>Microsoft Visual Studio:</strong> Our development IDE for building this ASP.NET Core project.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>ASP.NET Core:</strong> The robust framework that powers our web application and handles HTTP requests.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Razor Pages:</strong> The foundation of our web pages, combining C# code-behind and HTML templates.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>HTML, CSS, JavaScript:</strong> These core web technologies shape the appearance and interactivity of our site.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Bootstrap:</strong> Our secret to responsive and modern UI design, ensuring a delightful user experience.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>JSON:</strong> The format we use to store and manage data for displaying our exquisite furniture products.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>C#:</strong> The language powering our server-side logic, making the magic happen behind the scenes.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>.NET Core:</strong> The backbone of our application, empowering our ASP.NET Core web project.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <p class="lead">
        Let's begin the journey of transforming your living spaces into something extraordinary!
        Start exploring our collection and discover the furniture pieces that resonate with your style.
    </p>

    <p>
        Learn more about <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/aspnet/core">building Web apps with ASP.NET Core</a>.
    </p>
</div>
